OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fbecoming largely clear, although low
OL,7,Fcloud may creep across western areas,
OL,8,Fespecially Derbyshire where a little
OL,9,Fdrizzle may develop over the Peak
OL,10,FDistrict.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy, with morning drizzle
OL,13,For light rain across the Peak District
OL,14,Fany hill fog lifting with showers
OL,15,Flater. Elsewhere sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Feeling warm, but breezy
OL,17,Fin places.
