OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FGenerally large amounts of cloud,
OL,7,Falthough some bright or prolonged
OL,8,Fsunny spells will occur. Occasionally
OL,9,Fbreezy, and becoming warm or very warm
OL,10,Fas temperatures are likely to
OL,11,Fgradually increase.
